  "history": {
    "en": "The Birman is a docile, quiet cat who loves people and will follow them from room to room. Expect the Birman to want to be involved in what you’re doing. He communicates in a soft voice, mainly to remind you that perhaps it’s time for dinner or maybe for a nice cuddle on the sofa. He enjoys being held and will relax in your arms like a furry baby.",
    "zh": "伯曼猫是一种温顺、安静的猫咪，热爱人类，会跟随主人从一个房间到另一个房间。它们希望参与你正在做的事情。它们用柔和的声音交流，主要是提醒你也许是时候吃晚餐了，或者想在沙发上好好依偎一下。它们喜欢被抱着，会像毛茸茸的婴儿一样在你怀里放松。"
  },
